        content: { es: "La cocina escocesa ha evolucionado enormemente. Aunque el haggis sigue siendo emblematico, encontraras mariscos frescos de las costas, carne de caza de las Highlands, salmon ahumado de primera calidad y pastelerias tradicionales que te sorprenderan.", en: "Scottish cuisine has evolved enormously. Although haggis remains emblematic, you'll find fresh seafood from the coasts, game meat from the Highlands, first-quality smoked salmon, and traditional pastries that will surprise you.", pt: "A culinaria escocesa evoluiu enormemente. Embora o haggis ainda seja emblematico, voce encontrara frutos do mar frescos da costa, carne de caca das Highlands, salmao defumado de primeira qualidade e doces tradicionais que vao te surpreender." },
